{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>某国为了防御敌国的导弹袭击，开发出一种导弹拦截系统，但是这种拦截系统有一个缺陷：虽然它的第一发炮弹能够到达任意的高度，但是以后每一发炮弹都不能高于前一发的高度。某天，雷达捕捉到敌国的导弹来袭，由于该系统还在试用阶段。所以一套系统有可能不能拦截所有的导弹。<p><p>输入导弹依次飞来的高度（雷达给出的高度不大于30000的正整数）。计算要拦截所有导弹最小需要配备多少套这种导弹拦截系统。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"拦截导弹问题 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>要拦截所有导弹最小配备的系统数k。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>n颗依次飞来的高度（1≤n≤1000）。<p>","examples":"<input>389 207 155 300 299 170 158 65\n</input><output>2\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"输入：导弹高度： 4  3  2\n输出：导弹拦截系统k=1\n","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1322","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}